<i>adjective</i>: 험악하다 [허ː마카다], 엄숙하다 [엄수카다], 심각하다 [심ː가카다], 무겁다 [무겁따], 근엄하다 [그ː넘하다] <i>noun</i>: 육수 [육쑤], 산소 [산소], 무덤 [무덤], 묘지 [묘ː지], 묘소 [묘ː소] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>험악하다 [허ː마카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wild; rough; tough</dd><br>
<dd>땅의 모양, 기후 등이 거칠고 나쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>The shape of the ground, climate, etc., being rough and bad.</dd><br>
<dd>2. bad; ugly; grave</dd><br>
<dd>분위기나 상태 등이 매우 나쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>The atmosphere or circumstances being very bad.</dd><br>
<dd>3. menacing; threatening</dd><br>
<dd>성격, 태도, 생김새 등이 사납고 나쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>A personality, attitude, appearance, etc., being wild and bad.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄숙하다 [엄수카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. solemn; grave; serious</dd><br>
<dd>의식이나 분위기 등이 무겁고 조용하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A ceremony, atmosphere, etc., being heavy and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>2. solemn; grave; serious</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 태도 등이 무겁고 점잖다.</dd><br>
<dd>A speech, attitude, etc., being heavy and refined.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심각하다 [심ː가카다]</dt><br>
<dd>serious; grave</dd><br>
<dd>상태나 정도가 매우 심하거나 절박하거나 중대하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or degree being very severe, urgent, or important.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무겁다 [무겁따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heavy; weighty</dd><br>
<dd>무게가 많이 나가다.</dd><br>
<dd>Weighing a lot.</dd><br>
<dd>2. important; grave</dd><br>
<dd>책임이나 맡은 역할이 크고 중요하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being great and important in terms of one's responsibility or role.</dd><br>
<dd>3. heavy; grave</dd><br>
<dd>잘못이나 죄가 크다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being big and serious in terms of one's fault or crime.</dd><br>
<dd>4. heavy</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 빠져 움직이기가 어렵고 힘들다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being leaden and laborious due to a lack of vitality.</dd><br>
<dd>5. heavy</dd><br>
<dd>움직임이 둔하고 느리다.</dd><br>
<dd>Slow and sluggish in movement.</dd><br>
<dd>6. heavy; depressed</dd><br>
<dd>기분이나 분위기 등이 유쾌하지 못하고 어둡고 답답하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Heavy-hearted and dismal, not being cheerful in terms of mood, atmosphere, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>7. heavy; serious</dd><br>
<dd>소리가 명랑하지 않고 심각하거나 색깔 등이 어둡다.</dd><br>
<dd>Serious, not being light in sound, or dark in color, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>8. heavy; burdensome</dd><br>
<dd>벌이나 벌금 등이 부담이 될 정도로 심하고 많다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being great in degree or quantity in terms of punishment, fine, etc., putting too much burden on someone.</dd><br>
<dd>9. heavy</dd><br>
<dd>임신으로 배가 불러서 움직이기 힘들다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being difficult to move around due to pregnancy.</dd><br>
<dd>10. important; significant</dd><br>
<dd>아주 중요하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Extremely important.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>근엄하다 [그ː넘하다]</dt><br>
<dd>grave; austere</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 태도가 신중하고 엄숙하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's look or behavior being discreet and serious.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>육수 [육쑤]</dt><br>
<dd>meat stock; grave</dd><br>
<dd>고기를 삶은 국물.</dd><br>
<dd>The soup without meat or other solid ingredients that is made by boiling water with meat.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>산소 [산소]</dt><br>
<dd>1. grave; tomb</dd><br>
<dd>(높이는 말로) 사람의 무덤.</dd><br>
<dd>(polite form) A person's tomb.</dd><br>
<dd>2. graveyard; burial ground</dd><br>
<dd>무덤이 있는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place with a grave.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무덤 [무덤]</dt><br>
<dd>grave</dd><br>
<dd>죽은 사람의 몸이나 유골을 땅에 묻어 놓은 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>An underground place where the body or bones of a dead person are buried.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>묘지 [묘ː지]</dt><br>
<dd>1. grave; tomb</dd><br>
<dd>죽은 사람의 몸이나 유골을 땅에 묻어 놓은 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place for burying the body or remains of a dead person beneath the ground.</dd><br>
<dd>2. graveyard; cemetery; burial ground</dd><br>
<dd>무덤이 있는 땅.</dd><br>
<dd>A land used for burying the dead.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>묘소 [묘ː소]</dt><br>
<dd>grave; tomb</dd><br>
<dd>무덤이 있는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place with a grave.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>